      "toolCallId": "e4",
      "output": "# 9-2-3 Jobs — Site Analysis\n\n## Identity\n9-2-3 Jobs is an award-winning UK recruitment consultancy specialising in\n**part-time, hybrid and fractional roles** for senior professionals.\n\nTagline: \"THE RECRUITMENT CONSULTANCY for Part-Time, Hybrid and Fractional roles\"\n\nFounder: Helen Wright (helen@923jobs.com)\n\n## Navigation (existing site)\n- /about-923, /ourethos, /our-story, /our-awards, /meet-the-team\n- /ourservices, /why-choose-us, /how-we-work\n- /flexibleworkingresources, /what-is-flexible-working\n- /jobshomepage, /resources-for-candidates\n- /diversity-inclusion-and-shortlisting\n- /eventsandpress, /podcasts-, /news-, /blog-9-2-3\n- /whatourclientssay, /our-candidates\n- /get-in-touch, /contact-us\n- /923-book-club, /privacypolicy, /harassment, /faqs\n\n## Socials\n- facebook.com/923jobs\n- linkedin.com/company/10661519\n- instagram.com/923jobs\n\n## Ethos quote\n\"We are an award-winning recruitment consultancy passionate about\nbreaking the conventions of the traditional 9-to-5.\"",
      "isError": false,
      "isCollapsed": true
    },
